    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the processes of preparing, curing, or purposely transforming materials, such as clay, silica, or glass, by means of heat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
